<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.3.9">
<l>eṉceykē ṉaṭiyēṉu raiyī ritaṟkeṉṟu meṉmaṉat tēyiruk kumpukaḻ</l>
<l>tañcaiyā ḷiyaippoṉ peyarōṉ neñcamaṉṟi ṭantava ṉaittaḻa lēpurai</l>
<l>miñceyvā ḷarakkaṉ nakarpāḻ paṭaccūḻka ṭalciṟai vaittimai yōrtoḻum</l>
<l>poṉceymāl varaiyai maṇikkuṉṟi ṉaiyaṉṟi yeṉmaṉam pōṟṟiyeṉ ṉātē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tell [me], what should I, his servant, do for this [grace]?</l>
<l rend="indent">Without the ruler of famed Tañcai who is always in my heart,</l>
<l>The one who once dug into the chest of the one named ‘Gold,’</l>
<l>The huge mountain made of gold, adored by the celestials,</l>
<l rend="indent">having put a wall in the surrounding sea</l>
<l>To lay low the city of the demon with a sword that produced fire-like sparks,</l>
<l rend="indent">that jeweled peak, my mind expresses no praises.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
